<div class="title">Still Can't Sleep</div>
<div class="substance">AMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=DJ+Devin&Exact=1">DJ Devin</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; DJ Devin. "Still Can't Sleep: An Experience with AMT (exp41190)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 21, 2008. erowid.org/exp/41190</div>

<br/>



